Model @Kenya_Jones and actor @WillPeltz tied the knot on June 13, 2026, at Will’s family’s home in Mt. Kisco, New York — the same place he proposed. Will recalls the ceremony as “the perfect moment," and the reception that followed was filled with dancing, celebrating, and some impromptu watching of the Knicks securing the NBA Championship, which led to a massive group rush to the dance floor after the final buzzer. “I felt completely present with Will throughout, which was all that I hoped for,” Kenya says about the celebration. Head to the link in our bio for a look inside the couple’s celebration and all of the details.
